{"tid":2247684,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青衣及牛頭角 兩男女先後墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-10-18T05:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T05:30:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8183e30f66c64066e22845712a6f0036f4f41ca4","tid":2247684,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"青衣長安邨安江樓，清晨6時許，保安報案指一名男子倒卧大廈簷篷昏迷，懷疑他墮樓。救護員接報到場，檢查後證實他已死亡。警方未有撿獲遺書，調查後相信該名33歲姓周男子由某樓層走廊墮下。<br />\n<br />\n另外，凌晨2時許，一名83歲姓殷老婦，於牛頭角上邨常逸樓高處墮下，倒卧大廈對開昏迷，住戶聽到巨響報案。救護員接報到場，經檢驗證實已經死亡。警方撿獲遺書，調查後相信女事主由單位墮下。據知她有身體病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201018/NJWQHYBCRFF4NFHK3IAO4OJFBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201018%2FNJWQHYBCRFF4NFHK3IAO4OJFBE%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=8d2d9c56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201018%2FNJWQHYBCRFF4NFHK3IAO4OJFBE%2F&h=d1ac4d62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201018/NJWQHYBCRFF4NFHK3IAO4OJFBE/</a>"},{"pid":"eb787226ba4385b9acc7936fe704d1f9b82041de","tid":2247684,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a698b5664f6f1791fc8db3ebae07ed16d011f7c","tid":2247684,"uid":103809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"兩單冇關係又唔分開報..."},{"pid":"7a28f6c6469438466fe12503f2d6749a097b97cc","tid":2247684,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"安息"},{"pid":"373dd32930688b337e76b40839009d864f3db0fd","tid":2247684,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4a698b5664f6f1791fc8db3ebae07ed16d011f7c","tid":2247684,"uid":103809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re